# Sprint 30 Bucket GG — Fastlane plugin manifest.
#
# `supply` (Play Store deploy action `upload_to_play_store`) ships in
# fastlane-core, so it does NOT need to be listed here. This file exists
# so future plugin additions (e.g. fastlane-plugin-versioning,
# fastlane-plugin-appcenter) have a canonical home and `bundle install`
# / `fastlane install_plugins` keeps Gemfile.lock in sync.
#
# To add a plugin:
#   1. `fastlane add_plugin <name>`         (writes to this file)
#   2. `bundle install`                      (resolves Gemfile + plugins)
#   3. Commit Pluginfile + Gemfile.lock changes.

